$ Database requirements

Some ~functional requirements~ that an → development/databases/DBMS/RDMBS should meet include
  • Store *any* kind of → development/Data, → development/Data#un_structured-data[structured, unstructured, binary …]
  • Support → development/databases/common/ACID properties
  • deal with complex relationship between data items
  • maintain the database schemata to meet business requirements
  • → development/databases/SQL interface
  • reports in various file formats
  • depending on a user's role, data should be presented accordingly
  • concurrent use

~Non functional requirements~ include
  • Ensuring → development/Data/quality and data integrity
  • high availability
  • disaster recoverability
  • scalability
  • security
  • ease of software patching and installing new versions
  • backup/recovery
